00:33:27,850 --> 00:33:30,010
Go ahead. Go ahead.

375
00:33:30,010 --> 00:33:32,210
Look at several hundred-mile radii around this small area.

376
00:33:32,210 --> 00:33:35,050
See if this is the only place.

377
00:33:35,050 --> 00:33:39,550
I'm afraid that there won't even be one single room by the time you come back.

378
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:48,380
If so, then one bedroom it is.

379
00:33:48,380 --> 00:33:50,400
Okay.

